content:
RATP may refer to:
Transportation:

RATP Group, or Régie Autonome des Transports Parisiens, a public transport operator based in Paris, France
RATP Iași (Regia Autonomă de Transport Public Iași), a transit operator responsible for public transportation in Iași, Romania
RATP Ploiești (Regia Autonomă de Transport Public Ploiești), a transit operator responsible for public transportation in Ploiești, RomaniaComputation:

Reliable Asynchronous Transfer Protocol (RATP), defined in RFC 916
